title: Barnette slams GOP rivals at closed event as spotlight on late-surging Pennsylvania Senate hopeful intensifies - CNN
content:
1. Barnette slams GOP rivals at closed event as spotlight on late-surging Pennsylvania Senate hopeful intensifies  CNN

  3. Dr. Oz called out an Islamophobic tweet from a GOP opponent who said 'Pedophilia is a Cornerstone of Islam'  Yahoo News

description: Pennsylvania Senate candidate Kathy Barnette slammed her Republican primary rivals on Saturday as being overly fixated on her surging candidacy, according to audio of a speech obtained by CNN, while calling her leading opponents "two globalists" who were only pandering to conservatives to get elected.
